settings.title: EstablishmentÔºöSeamless transition from urban commuting to off - road exploration.
settings.content: The launch of EB7 2.0 marks the genesis of our brand, symbolizing our pioneering spirit in the electric bicycle domain. It embodies our aspirations for transformation in the realm of transportation. From humble beginnings in a small warehouse, shaping the future of Jasion with just a wrench, to now having sold over 100,000 units of EB7 2.0, with a user base exceeding 80,000. This journey epitomizes our commitment to innovation and excellence, propelling us to redefine the electric bicycle experience.

settings.title: Design
settings.content: EB7 2.0 is crafted for style and versatility, seamlessly transitioning from urban commuting to off-road exploration. Its stylish design and robust construction reflect our pursuit of excellence and durability. Equipped with ergonomic handlebars, adjustable seats, and integrated LED display screens, every detail is meticulously designed to enhance aesthetics and performance. EB7 2.0 demonstrates our unwavering commitment to quality and innovation.

settings.title: Craftsmanship
settings.content: Each EB7 2.0 embodies our dedication to craftsmanship and engineering excellence. From precise frame welding to assembly of motor components, meticulous attention to detail ensures 100% safety certification for the bicycle in both structure and function. Constructed with premium materials and steady technology, EB7 2.0 maintains durability and reliability, safeguarding every consumer's journey.

settings.title: Finished Product
settings.content: EB7 2.0 represents our craftsmanship in seamlessly integrating folding commuting and adventurous off-road attributes into one bicycle. It disrupts traditional modes of bicycle travel, serving as a gateway to new experiences and limitless possibilities. Get ready to ride into the future with EB7 2.0 and experience unparalleled joy with electric bicycles. Join the thousands of riders embracing EB7 2.0, exploring the freedom and excitement that awaits in every journey.

settings.text_sub: Jasion EB7 all-terrain electric bike is an affordable e-bike. A sustained 500W brushless geared hub motor allows you to ride freely through the city blocks and dirt roads just like the breeze. 55 miles on a single charge, 20'' √ó 3.0'' Fat Tires, and double shock absorption, all for safer and smoother cycling.

settings.title: Equipped with a Powerful 850W Motor
settings.content: Delivering 48 Nm of torque within just 2 seconds in the 5-speed setting. The motor, designed with a sine wave structure, allows you to effortlessly control your riding speed across gears 1 to 5, providing a customizable and intuitive riding experience.

settings.title: Samsung/LG 48V10A Battery
settings.content: Utilizing the newly developed 18650 battery cells from Samsung SDI, each lithium-ion single cell measures 18mm in diameter and 65mm in length, combining to form a 48V10A configuration. Jasion Bike incorporates a quick-detachable sealed design achieving an IPX-6 waterproof rating. The battery is removable for charging and holds UL 2271 international certification.

settings.title: 5 Driving Modes: Effortlessly Handle Various Road Conditions
settings.content: Delivering 48 Nm of torque within just 2 seconds in the 5-speed setting. The motor, designed with a sine wave structure, allows you to effortlessly control your riding speed across gears 1 to 5, providing a customizable and intuitive riding experienceÔºå JasionBike rear hub motor has obtained international certification according to ISO 2849 standards.

settings.title: Efficient Performance: 55-Mile Range on a Single Charge
settings.content: Utilizing Samsung SDI's newly developed 21750 cells, each lithium-ion cell has a diameter of 21 millimeters and a length of 75 millimeters, forming a 48V10A configuration. The 21750 battery cell capacity is increased by 35%, and its volume energy density is nearly 20% higher than the original 18650 cells. Jasion Bike employs a quick-detach sealed design for the battery, with multiple layers of protective sheathing achieving an IPX-6 waterproof rating. The battery features removable charging.

settings.text_sub: If range anxiety is of concern to you, Rhino will get you covered with its 1440wh battery capacity. Battery density has increased 21% from 18,650 to 21,700 cells, allowing you to ride up to 100 miles for a single charge. And worried about long charging times? It takes only 5 hours to get fully charged with 2 chargers.

settings.title: Fold easily for convenient transportation and storage.
settings.content: Jasion Bike takes pride in its cutting-edge quick multi-stage disassembly design. With no need for cumbersome tools, just a few simple steps allow for the rapid disassembly of various components, ensuring easy portability and storage.

settings.title: Enjoy a Smooth and Comfortable Ride
settings.content: Jasion Bike electric bike features a front and rear manually adjustable damping shock absorption system crafted from high-durability materials, ensuring stability over extended usage. Whether navigating city streets, tackling off-road mountain trails, or traversing bumpy paths, the system seamlessly adapts to various terrains through easy manual adjustments, providing a stable and comfortable ride in any scenario.

settings.title: Closed, Concealed Battery Design
settings.content: This bike is equipped with a 48V 11.6Ah lithium-ion battery and an 1000W motor. The enclosed design achieves an IPX-6 waterproof rating, providing better protection for the battery cells and preventing theft. Aipas batteries are internationally certified with UL 2849, ensuring a longer lifespan and larger capacity, with a full charge offering a range of up to 55 miles.

settings.title: 20" x 3" Puncture-Resistant Tires
settings.content: The high-quality fat tires provide extra protection against punctures from thorns, glass, and other small materials.

settings.title: Adjustable Front and Rear Suspension Setup
settings.content: Equipped with a front fork suspension and rear suspension, absorbs most jarring bumps and shocks when riding, and provides another riding experience.

settings.title: Headlight&Taillight
settings.content: Brighter LED headlights, make riding more convenient and safer. The integrated taillight will flash when brake, making it a warning light at night.

settings.title: Shimano 7-Speed & Motorcycle-Style Hand-Twist Throttle
settings.content: The Shimano 7-speed gear shifter makes your ride smoother, and the motorcycle-style hand-twist throttle allows for easy control of the electric bike's speed.

settings.title: Foldable Electric Bike
settings.content: The foldable and portable design makes the EB7 e-bike easy to carry and fits stock into any compact space, such as an apartment, subway, or car trunk.Folding Size: 36*21*29 (Inch)

settings.title: Dual Disc Brake System
settings.content: The sensitive brake system with the front and rear 160mm disc rotors can provide sufficient braking force at a short distance whether in wet or dry conditions.

settings.title: Foldable Footrests
settings.content: EB7 2.0 in order to make it more convenient for users to fold and place the back of the car, so the pedals made an innovative breakthrough, the pedals folded to make the electric bike more stable and less prone to bumps.

settings.title: What's your shipping policy?
settings.content:
Jasion has suspended local pick-up services in the United States. If pick-up services are resumed, we will update the information on our website. Please check the website for updates.

We provide UPS, USPS, and FedEx shipping services. No tax is needed. We DO NOT ship to PO BOXES.

In-stock orders typically ship within 2 business days, unless otherwise noted on the product page. Please allow 5-7 business days for your shipment to arrive at your address. Any delivery dates provided by JASION are estimates.

For more shipping information, send an email to support@Jasionbike.com. We will get back to you in 24 hours.

Want to know more about shipping policies, please check more details on our Shipping Policy Page.

settings.title: What's your warranty policy?
settings.content:
All JASION bikes carry a one(1) year warranty from the date of receipt of the bike for manufacturing defects in materials and/or workmanship( all free accessories are not covered).

We will replace any component that is defective or damaged in materials and/or workmanship( including the damage in the processing of shipment).

Before making a warranty claim, we suggest that you first contact us at support@jasionbike.com.

Want to know more about warranty policies, please check more details on our Warranty Policy Page.

settings.title: What's your return&refund policy?
settings.content:
We provide exchange service within 14 days. If the product is defective or damaged, Send damaged photos or videos to customer service within 14 days after receiving the goods, and the damaged parts can be replaced or compensated. We will cover the return (exchange) shipping costs.

In the case of non-quality returns, the customer will be responsible for the return shipping costs.

You can always contact us for any return questions at support@jasionbike.com.

Want to know more about return and refound policies, please check more details on our Return&Refund Policy Page.

settings.title: Does my height suit EB7 2.0?
settings.content: The recommended rider height is 5'1"-6'2".

settings.title: How long does it take to fully charge the battery?
settings.content: It will take 4-5 hours.

settings.title: How long will it take for my shipment to arrive?
settings.content: Generally, your order will be shipped within one business day after the order is placed, and package shipping will take approximately 3-5 days.

settings.title: What is the difference between EB7 2.0 and EB7 ST?
settings.content: The EB7 ST has a new design step-through with a lower span than before, it is more suitable for older people or people with physical limitations to ride.

settings.title: Does my Jasion ebike come pre-assembled?
settings.content: Your e-bike arrives 95% assembled. There are just a few pieces to put into place once you take the bike out of the box. For unboxing and setup instructions, please follow the guides on our YouTube Channel.

settings.title: My Camp Bike Jasion EB7.
settings.content: I love this Jasion eb7 bike and it's well-built and rides smoothly. The bike comes with a 1-year warranty and a manual with all the necessary information. The battery takes four to five hours to fully charge and can be charged while still attached to the bike. It's worth buying!
